@HostAddress = http://localhost:5237

### Recommend mixes
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/mixes/recommend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "dark rolling dnb around 174bpm",
  "maxResults": 3
}

###

### Recommend mixes — genre query
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/mixes/recommend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "house music",
  "maxResults": 5
}

###

### Browse catalog grouped by genre
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/catalog?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Browse mixes ordered by date
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/catalog/mixes?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Browse artists by track recurrence
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/catalog/artists?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Browse deduplicated tracks
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/catalog/tracks?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Mixes by artist name
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/catalog/artists/Calibre/mixes
Accept: application/json

###

### Health check
GET {{HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###
